Notes: College of the Ozarks overcomes a 10-point deficit in the first half and holds
off a late UMR rally to hand the Lady Miners their first loss of the season...
UMR closed to within one with 12 seconds to go, but the Bobcats hit 4-4 at the
line to close out the game...Ozarks was 33-34 at the line in the game.
Game.Officials: John Murray,  Jim Brickey,  Sandra Cunningham
